className.description: Class names applied to the element or a function that returns them based on the component's state.

defaultOpen.description: If true, the Collapsible is initially open. This is the uncontrolled counterpart of open.

onOpenChange.description: Callback fired when the Collapsible is opened or closed.

open.description: If true, the Collapsible is initially open. This is the controlled counterpart of defaultOpen.

render.description: A function to customize rendering of the component.
